Name: Chevy 410 Sprint Car Racing Engine | Custom-Built Aluminum SBC
Description:
• Aluminum 410 Chevy Small Block Sprint Car engine designed and built by championship winning engine builders
  • State of the art machining and components
  • Built to your specifications whether for the weekly show or national tour
  • We build for winged and non-winged Sprint Cars
  • Balanced and Blue Printed
  • Dyno sheet with every engine
  • May vary from photo
  • Shown with upgraded options
  • Engine is designed and built to customer needs, call to order

Decades of Proven Performance on the Track

The 410 Cubic Inch Aluminum Small Block engine is synonymous with the top tier of Sprint Car racing, and Speedway Motors is a name synonymous with winning in dirt track racing for over 60 years.

Born from the legendary Speedway Motors #4x Cars tearing up tracks from the ’60s through the ’80s, and still growing today, Speedway Motors Racing Engines are winning A features and championships in Sprint Cars, Late Models and Stock Cars across the country.

State of the Art Manufacturing and Custom Designed for your Race Program

Our 410 Cubic Inch Aluminum Sprint Car Engine is designed for your specific racing needs; machined and lightened with CNC precision. These engines are then hand built with premium components by championship winning engine builders in our own facilities right here in Lincoln, Nebraska.

Dyno tested and precision tuned before shipping, our 410 Sprint car engines deliver the power you need, whether you’re screaming down the straights at Knoxville, or digging out of the corner in a non-wing sprinter. Speedway Motors Racing Engines will build your 410 engine to stand above the competition in any Sprint Car series.

950 Horsepower, 730 lb-ft of Torque

The Speedway Motors Racing Engines Aluminum 410 Sprint Engine was featured in the 2020 National Sprint Car Hall of Fame Raffle Race Car. You can see the car come together in our 410 Sprint Car Build series on The Toolbox. This engine wasn’t produced for looks—it was produced to win.

The dyno did not lie. Our 410 Sprint Car engine produced 949.9 horsepower at 7,200 rpm and 729.8 lb-ft of torque at 5,700 rpm. This is not just a dyno queen, it is ready for night after night of competition. Check out the build and the dyno pull .

Each Speedway Motors Racing Engines Aluminum 410 Sprint Engine has its piston rings and camshaft broken in on our in-house engine dyno using a specific break in oil to ensure proper break in and protection, then the engine is given final tuning and is dyno tested. You will receive a dyno sheet showing the horsepower and torque of your specific engine, as well as engine settings like lash, timing, and fuel and oil used.

We build each engine to your specifications so the dyno results will vary.

Ready for Competition

Winged or non-winged, weekly or the national tour, contact us to start building the right 410 Sprint Car engine for you. We have all the parts, from the block and internals, down to the cylinder heads, and more, in stock and ready for us to build your new race winning bullet! It will be shipped competition ready, blue printed, balanced, dyno tested and ready to drop in.

Name: LS Classic GMLS9012 LS3 Tri-Power Crate Engine, Chrome BBC Style
Description:
All of our LS Classic components are available, installed, on one of our Classic Crate Engines. We start with a brand new, GM 495 horse power LS3 right out of the box and with a two year warranty. We then paint it orange (if you so desire) and begin assembling your desired components until we have the perfect crate engine for your project. Once completely assembled we put the engine on our in-house run stand, load your Holley EFI ECU with our start-up tune, and run your engine to check for leaks and oil pressure. After we are satisfied that your engine will operate with no issues, we put it back in the original GM crate and ship it directly to you or your builder. Once you receive your engine it is as simple as installing the engine, routing the Holley wiring harness, terminating a couple of power and ground wires, and putting fuel pressure to the engine. We guarantee an easy start up!

All Crate Engines include:

  • New GM LS3 495 HP Crate Engine with two year warranty
  • Painted orange or unpainted
  • Holley Terminator engine management system with O2 sensor and trans control
  • Corvette water pump, thermostat housing, and balancer
  • High performance rear dump exhaust manifolds
  • 14" automatic transmission flexplate

Name: Edelbrock 46127 Supercharged Gen III 426 Hemi with Accessories
Description:
Edelbrock 426 c.i.d. HEMI crate engine Part #46126 produces an astounding 808 horsepower and 762 ft-lbs. of torque. The foundation is based on a new iron Mopar 392 block with a forged Manley crankshaft, forged Manley H-Beam connecting rods and forged aluminum pistons. Sitting on top is an Edelbrock E-Force supercharger system with Eaton TVS R2650 rotors. Also included are the essential supercharger kit components, such as the electric intercooler water pump, intercooler plumbing, intercooler recovery tank, as well as fuel rails, fuel injectors, coils, mass air flow sensor (MAFS) housing, and reusable air filter.

The supercharger equipped on this engine features a driver's side throttle body orientation for ease of intake routing. Pair with universal heat exchangers for a complete installation.

Engine Specifications:

  • Displacement: 426 c.i.d.
  • Bore: 4.090"
  • Stroke: 4.050"
  • Horsepower: 808
  • Torque: 762
  • Compression: 9.9:1
  • Block: New Mopar Iron
  • Crankshaft: Forged 4340
  • Pistons: Forged Aluminum -5cc
  • Camshaft: 226°/234°, .619/.612, 114 cl
  • Rocker Arms: Stock Gen III Hemi
  • Cylinder Heads: Edelbrock Performer RPM #61099
  • Fuel Injectors: 60 lb./hr., Siemens
  • Supercharger: Edelbrock E-Force R2650 TVS
  • Supercharger Belt: 100” 6-Rib
  • Fuel Type: Requires 91 Octane Minimum

Name: Edelbrock 49557 Edelbrock/Musi 555 RPM XT EFI 723 HP
Description:
The Edelbrock/Musi 555 Pro-Flo 4 XT is the most powerful package in our line and features the Pro-Flo 4 XT electronic fuel injection. The Pro-Flo 4 XT EFI system consists of a front mount 90mm throttle body design manifold with a large plenum and tapered runners that deliver more horsepower and torque than a traditional single-plane intake manifold. The system also includes fuel injectors, fuel rails, throttle body, electronic engine control unit (ECU).

Like the Pro-Flo 4 single-plane application, this engine is ready to run right out of the crate with pre-loaded calibrations. The E-Tuner app uses a Bluetooth wireless connection to communicate with the ECU’s self-learning capability to continually adjust the calibration to get the maximum performance of your engine.

  • Cylinder Heads: E-CNC #79555
  • Distributor: Included
  • Valve Covers: Cast Aluminum
  • Warranty: 2-Year / Unlimited Mileage

Description:
Edelbrock Part #46725 is the same long-block used on their Victor Jr. LS 416 crate engine that makes 602 horsepower and 538 ft-lbs. of torque. It features an aluminum LS3 block with a forged and balanced Manley crankshaft, forged Manley H-Beam connecting rods and Manley forged aluminum pistons to create a 416ci LS3 stroker with 4.065" bore and 4.000" stroke. The core of this long-block are the Victor Jr. LS3 cylinder heads #61339 and Rollin' Thunder hydraulic roller camshaft #2219. These are the key components that help this engine deliver impressive power potential. Its compact profile makes this engine a great solution for a hassle-free LS swap into any high-performance muscle car, street rod or truck!

Name: Chevrolet Performance LS3/430 HP Connect and Cruise, 6L80E Trans
Description:
LS3 Connect and Cruise

The Chevrolet Performance Connect and Cruise is the quickest and easiest way to get your project hot rod or muscle car up and running. The Connect and Cruise kit have been designed and components carefully matched for optimal compatibility and performance, while also identifying the complementing engine and transmission controllers, and supporting installation kits.

A new classic – the LS3 Engine

As the standard engine in the fifth-generation Camaro SS and C6 Corvette, the high-revving, deep-breathing LS3 6.2L is poised to go down in history as one of Chevrolet’s best and most versatile engines.

The LS3 is filled with components designed for high performance and longevity. The aluminum block is filled with a sturdy reciprocating assembly that combines with L92-type rectangular-port heads to deliver a 10.7:1 compression ratio.

  • 6.2L
  • 376 C.I.D
  • 430 HP @ 5900 RPM
  • 425 LB/FT @ 4600 RPM
  • Aluminum Cylinder Head Material
  • Internal engine balance
  • 1-piece rear main seal style

6L80E - The Perfect Compliment

Developed with upgraded internal components, Chevrolet Performance’s SuperMatic 6L80-E 6-speed automatic transmission offers an exceptional torque rating of 650 lb.-ft. – a 45 percent increase over regular production versions of the 6-speed automatic.

A deep 4.02:1 first gear enables strong launch performance, while the 0.67:1 top gear supports balanced performance on the highway. It is designed for use with Chevrolet Performance’s LS and LSX crate engines in 2WD applications. The SuperMatic 6L80-E comes in two kits: one that includes a 2400-stall torque converter (P/N 19366637) and one that includes a 3000-stall converter (P/N 19417102).

  • 6-Speed Automatic
  • 650 Lb-Ft Torque Limit
  • 2400-2800 Stall Torque Converter
  • 4.02 1st Gear
  • 2.36 2nd Gear
  • 1.53 3rd Gear
  • 1.15 4th Gear
  • 0.85 5th Gear
  • 0.67 6th Gear

LS Controller Kit

Properly Tune Your GM Perfromance Crate Engine with this LS Controller Kit. Kit includes everything you need!

Includes:

  • ECU
  • Engine wiring harness
  • Mass airflow meter
  • Mass airflow meter mounting boss
  • Accelerator pedal assembly
  • Two oxygen sensors with mounting bosses
  • Detailed instruction sheet

LS Trans Install Kit

Chevrolet Performance Part has put together the exact kit you need to connect the GM 6L80E  transmission to your LS Engine build.

Included in this Kit:

(1) GM LS3 6.2 430HP Engine

(1) Chevy Performance 6l80E Transmission

(1) LS ECU Controller Kit

(1) LS Engine Trans Install Kit

  • 100% brand new, 383 short block with forged steel crankshaft
  • Powdered metal rods and hypereutectic pistons
  • Edelbrock E-TEC 200 heads
  • Rollin' Thunder hydraulic roller camshaft
  • Roller rocker arms
  • RPM Air-Gap intake manifold
  • Thunder Series AVS 800 cfm carburetor and short water pump
  • Unique to the SS383, the water pump, valve covers and air cleaner are styled with a black finish.
  • Valve covers are then laser engraved with Vic Edelbrock's signature and the engines serial number.
  • Only 250 will be made - get one while you still can.

  • Displacement: 383 c.i.d.
  • Horsepower: 460 hp
  • Torque: 460 ft-lbs.
  • Compression: 9.5:1
  • Block: NEW 383 4 bolt main with 1-piece rear main seal
  • Crankshaft: Forged steel
  • Pistons: Hypereutectic
  • Camshaft: Rollin' Thunder Hydraulic Roller #2207
  • Rocker Arms: 1.5:1 Roller
  • Manifold: RPM Air-Gap #75161
  • Cylinder Heads: Polished E-Tec 200 #609815
  • Carburetor: Thunder Series AVS
  • Water Pump: Victor Series aluminum
  • Distributor: Included
  • Valve Covers: Cast aluminum
  • Warranty: 2-year / Unlimited mileage

Description:
BluePrint Engines provides a Dyno Promise with results and bragging rights. They make sure they hit their target horsepower and proper torque with every crate engine, utilizing an advanced computerized balancer to get rotating assemblies within 2 grams, ensuring silky smooth power over the entire rpm range. According to BluePrint, that's precisely why their engines sound and run better than the competitors. Accompanying your BluePrint Engines Pro Series Chevy LS 427 c.i.d. 605 hp EFI base dressed long block crate engine will be a comprehensive, dyno-generated printout showing its critical specs. No more guessing what the real-world peak horsepower and torque ratings are. Any doubters in the crowd? Simply flash them your dyno results!

  • 605 Horsepower / 565 FT LBS
  • 11:1 Compression Ratio
  • Aluminum Heads
  • Hydraulic Roller Cam
  • Forged Crank
